Killer Kau of Tholukuthi fame has passed his matric. Killer Kau’s became a social media sensation when he posted his video where he was singing Tholukuthi. Euphonik saw the video and contacted Killer Kau, and they made the song within 24 hours featuring Mbali Sikwane, who covered the song and shared the video on Facebook. Today a lot of matric students got to know whether or not they passed their matric. Amongst the thousands of students who made it was Killer Kau real name Sakhile Hlatshwayo. DJ Euphonik posted on Twitter that the singer and dancer have passed matric and now the real work begins. He wrote: “.@killerkau passed matric!!! Let the games begin...AGAIN!!”   